<div class="container-fluid mt-5">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-7">
                <img style="width: 95%" src="~/Images/Food Diagram.png" alt="">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-5 mt-4">
                <div class="row ">
                    <div class="col-md-12">
                        <h2 class="text-center font-weight-bold">Make Your Daily, Weekly Or Monthly Food Plan</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-12 text-center mt-5">
                        <p style="font-size: 18px; color: #808080; text-align: justify">We will take care of your regular food routine. Just make a diet plan. Your ingredients with detailed recipe will be at your door at right time.Just follow the instructions and prepare your food in a short time period.Be a professionalchef to your family with our service.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-12 text-center mt-5">
                        <a href="@Url.Action("Index", "FoodPlan")" class="btn text-white buttonCss">Make My Diet Plan</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<div class="container-fluid">
    <div style="border-radius: 15px;" class="container bg px-5 ">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-5">
                <h1 class="text-light pt-5">Build Your Own Box</h1><br>
                <p>Customize your menu with our available recipe. You can customize any item adjusting your food interest. Suppose you want to add more calories in your ordered item . Just edit the ingredient list and submit.</p>
                <div class="text-center">
                    <br>
                    <a href="@Url.Action("Create", "Box")" class="btn text-white boxButton">Build My Box</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-7">
                <img class="foodImage" style="width: 95%;" src="~/Images/box.png" alt="">
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>
